{"tid":1035423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［下體大滿足］乙武洋匡再婚　未鄉妻23歲混血正妹背景曝光","createTime":"2019-02-24T15:09:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T22:05:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"afcd959cd47389997dc74cccaeac3a4901cce67d","tid":1035423,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aqTW5J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aqTW5J.png&h=3d24bf6b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/230821_c810e0d6f0b25cb114a5fa4522f7a63c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F230821_c810e0d6f0b25cb114a5fa4522f7a63c.png&h=38c0c657&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/24/230825_afe2dfc368e6d78f0a8b1bdc2e00d840.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F24%2F230825_afe2dfc368e6d78f0a8b1bdc2e00d840.png&h=b67a0a2d&s={SIZE}\" />先前爆出婚外情、更偷吃過50女的42歲日本《五體不滿足》作家乙武洋匡，即將要再婚了，而且對象是23歲混血正妹，還是公司的代表董事(代表取締役) 乙武洋匡的新戀人，是1995年6月12日生的岩澤直美，長的很像16歲花式滑冰運動員阿麗娜&middot;扎吉托娃(Alina Zagitova)，是乙武的早稻田大學學妹，目前休學中，父親是日本人、母親是捷克人，會說5國語言，目前在「株式會社Culmony」擔任代表董事，經營小孩子英文會話、多文化教學，乙武洋匡是在她的研習班上認識，雙方趣味相投，於是開始交往。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）想知道更多，一定要看&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190220/1520835/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190220%2F1520835%2F&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=db0711f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190220%2F1520835%2F&h=ff934df9\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190220/1520835/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i